# ğŸ® GameTimeConverter - Game Time Converter Tool (English)

## ğŸ“Œ Introduction
GameTimeConverter is a **Windows application** that converts **game time (EGT, UTC-2) into Taipei Time (TST, UTC+8), New York Time (EST/EDT, UTC-5/UTC-4), Seoul Time (KST, UTC+9), and Los Angeles Time (PST/PDT, UTC-8/UTC-7).**

ğŸ”¹ **Key Features**
- ğŸ® **Game Time Conversion**: Supports **EGT (UTC-2)** conversion to multiple time zones, including **TST (UTC+8), EST/EDT (UTC-5/UTC-4), KST (UTC+9), PST/PDT (UTC-8/UTC-7)**.
- â³ **Easy Input**: **Dropdown-based date and time selection**, no manual input required.
- ğŸŒ **Multi-Language Support**: Built-in **10 languages**, with **flag-based selection for quick switching**.
- ğŸ¨ **Smart UI Layout**: **Automatically aligns UI elements** for a clean and structured display.
- ğŸ•°ï¸ **24-Hour Time Format** for clear and accurate time conversion.

